<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">( {والوَعْنُ:</span> المَلْجَأُ) ، كالوَعْلِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(} وتَوَعَّنَتِ الإِبِلُ والغَنَمُ)</span> والدَّوابُّ: <span class="c2">(بَلَغَتْ غايَةَ السِّمَنِ)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(وقيلَ: بَدا فيهنَّ السِّمَنُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ أَبو زيْدٍ:</span> سَمِنَتْ مِن غيرِ أَنْ يَحُدَّ غايَةً.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ غيرُهُ:</span> سَمِنَتْ أَيامَ الرَّبيعِ فَهِيَ {مُتَوَعِّنة.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>(و) } تَوَعَّنَ <span class="c2">(الشَّيءَ: اسْتَوْعَبَهُ)</span> واسْتَوْفاهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[وغن]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>: <span class="c2">( {الوَغْنَةُ)</span> :) أَهْمَلَهُ الجوْهرِيُّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ ابنُ الأَعْرابيِّ:</span> هُوَ <span class="c2">(الحُبُّ الواسِعُ)</span> ؛<span class="c5">) وَفِي بعضِ النسخِ:</span> الجُبُّ بالجِيمِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">قالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(} والتَّوَغُّنُ: الإِقْدامُ فِي الحَرْبِ)</span> .<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(والتَّوَغُّنُ: الإصْرارُ على المَعاصِي.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
